---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base lang="en" title="Spady | Funnel Design for Marketing & Recruiting" description="I design funnels for customer acquisition and recruiting — across Meta ads, LINE and social. From local shops and SMEs to study-abroad and global businesses. Ex-Meta Marketing Pro, based in Otaru, Hokkaido, Japan.">
  <!-- 1. ファーストビュー：1画面で権威性・信頼性・専門性を完結 -->
  <div class="band dark">
    <section class="lp-hero">
      <img class="fv-logo rise d1" src="/logo.png?v=20260707-1519" alt="Spady" width="84" height="84" />
      <a class="lang-switch rise d1" href="/">日本語</a>
      <div class="wrap lp-hero-inner">
        <div class="lp-hero-text">
          <p class="eyebrow rise d1">Funnel Design for Marketing & Recruiting</p>
          <h1 class="rise d2">
            Ads, LINE and social,<br />
            connected into <em>one funnel</em>.
          </h1>
          <p class="lp-sub rise d3">
            From local shops and SMEs to study-abroad and global businesses,<br class="pc" />
            I design funnels for customer acquisition and recruiting — from real field experience.<br class="pc" />
            Based in Otaru, Hokkaido. Working online, nationwide and worldwide.
          </p>
          <!-- 権威性・数字（ファーストビュー内で完結） -->
          <div class="cred rise d4">
            <div class="cred-item cred-meta">
              <strong>Ex-Meta</strong>
              <span>Worked as a Marketing Pro at Meta</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cred-item">
              <strong class="c-num n-blue"><span class="cnt" data-target="80">80</span><i>+</i></strong>
              <span>Ad agencies supported at Meta</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cred-item">
              <strong class="c-num n-green"><span class="cnt" data-target="100">100</span><i>+</i></strong>
              <span>LINE official accounts built</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cred-item">
              <strong>Certified</strong>
              <span>L Message partner (on PR TIMES)</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="lp-btns rise d5">
            <a class="btn primary btn-big btn-shine" href="#contact">Book a Free Consultation</a>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-assure rise d5">Free consultation｜Fully online, timezone-friendly｜No pushy sales</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 宇宙から見た地球：自転＋飛行機の周回＋世界中の人 -->
        <div class="hero-visual rise d3" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 520 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <defs>
              <clipPath id="globeClip"><circle cx="260" cy="300" r="215" /></clipPath>
              <clipPath id="satClip"><circle cx="384" cy="142" r="32" /></clipPath>
              <radialGradient id="ocean" cx="34%" cy="28%" r="88%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#2f89c5" />
                <stop offset="35%" stop-color="#175a8d" />
                <stop offset="70%" stop-color="#0a3457" />
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#041627" />
              </radialGradient>
              <linearGradient id="landGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#6fae76" />
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#2f6349" />
              </linearGradient>
              <radialGradient id="terminator" cx="32%" cy="26%" r="95%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(0,0,0,0)" />
                <stop offset="55%" stop-color="rgba(0,0,0,0)" />
                <stop offset="82%" stop-color="rgba(2,8,14,0.45)" />
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(1,4,8,0.85)" />
              </radialGradient>
              <radialGradient id="flash" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(255,235,170,0.95)" />
                <stop offset="45%" stop-color="rgba(255,215,94,0.5)" />
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(255,215,94,0)" />
              </radialGradient>
              <radialGradient id="specular" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,0.3)" />
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,0)" />
              </radialGradient>
              <filter id="soft" x="-40%" y="-40%" width="180%" height="180%">
                <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="4" />
              </filter>
              <filter id="atmo" x="-40%" y="-40%" width="180%" height="180%">
                <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="7" />
              </filter>
            </defs>

            <!-- 飛行機の軌道 -->
            <path id="orbitPath" d="M 260,44 a 256,256 0 1,1 -0.01,0" fill="none" class="orbit-ring" />

            <!-- 大気の光 -->
            <circle cx="260" cy="300" r="221" class="atmo-glow" filter="url(#atmo)" />
            <circle cx="260" cy="300" r="216" class="atmo-line" />

            <!-- 海 -->
            <circle cx="260" cy="300" r="215" fill="url(#ocean)" />

            <!-- 回転する大陸と雲 -->
            <g clip-path="url(#globeClip)">
              <g class="spin-land">
                <g id="landTile" class="land">
                  <path d="M150,196 C158,168 190,150 214,152 C232,138 262,132 288,140 C318,128 352,132 372,146 C402,142 428,156 436,176 C448,196 434,214 414,214 C398,226 376,222 362,232 C344,242 328,234 316,244 C300,256 282,246 268,252 C246,262 224,250 212,238 C192,236 172,228 162,214 C152,208 146,202 150,196 Z" />
                  <path d="M298,250 C312,262 312,286 300,298 C288,286 286,262 298,250 Z" />
                  <ellipse cx="352" cy="284" rx="6" ry="4" />
                  <ellipse cx="369" cy="297" rx="5" ry="3.5" />
                  <ellipse cx="385" cy="287" rx="4" ry="3" />
                  <ellipse cx="347" cy="305" rx="3.5" ry="2.5" />
                  <ellipse cx="421" cy="205" rx="3.5" ry="5" transform="rotate(28 421 205)" />
                  <ellipse cx="427" cy="218" rx="3" ry="4.5" transform="rotate(24 427 218)" />
                  <ellipse cx="423" cy="230" rx="2.5" ry="3.5" transform="rotate(18 423 230)" />
                  <path d="M180,262 C202,248 232,254 240,276 C250,300 244,336 228,368 C218,392 200,404 188,398 C176,384 168,352 166,322 C160,296 164,274 180,262 Z" />
                  <ellipse cx="252" cy="354" rx="4" ry="8" transform="rotate(16 252 354)" />
                  <path d="M96,132 C112,122 132,128 134,144 C132,158 116,164 102,158 C92,150 88,140 96,132 Z" />
                  <path d="M18,150 C44,124 92,120 116,142 C132,158 122,180 104,190 C92,206 74,216 60,232 C46,242 30,234 24,214 C10,192 6,168 18,150 Z" />
                  <path d="M74,238 C84,246 82,258 74,264 C66,256 66,244 74,238 Z" />
                  <path d="M84,268 C108,258 124,276 120,304 C116,342 100,378 84,394 C72,380 66,342 68,308 C66,286 72,274 84,268 Z" />
                  <path d="M352,392 C372,378 404,384 414,402 C418,420 396,434 372,430 C354,426 344,406 352,392 Z" />
                  <ellipse cx="434" cy="430" rx="2.5" ry="4" transform="rotate(24 434 430)" />
                </g>
                <use href="#landTile" x="464" />
                <use href="#landTile" x="-464" />
              </g>
              <g class="spin-clouds" filter="url(#soft)">
                <g id="cloudTile" class="clouds">
                  <ellipse cx="80" cy="182" rx="48" ry="11" />
                  <ellipse cx="212" cy="152" rx="60" ry="13" />
                  <ellipse cx="332" cy="222" rx="52" ry="11" />
                  <ellipse cx="142" cy="332" rx="58" ry="12" />
                  <ellipse cx="302" cy="362" rx="64" ry="13" />
                  <ellipse cx="404" cy="300" rx="40" ry="9" />
                  <ellipse cx="42" cy="286" rx="34" ry="9" />
                  <ellipse cx="238" cy="452" rx="56" ry="12" />
                  <ellipse cx="118" cy="252" rx="44" ry="10" />
                  <ellipse cx="356" cy="152" rx="42" ry="9" />
                  <ellipse cx="196" cy="408" rx="48" ry="10" />
                </g>
                <use href="#cloudTile" x="464" />
                <use href="#cloudTile" x="-464" />
              </g>
            </g>

            <!-- 昼夜の陰影・ハイライト -->
            <circle cx="260" cy="300" r="215" fill="url(#terminator)" />
            <ellipse cx="185" cy="205" rx="120" ry="90" fill="url(#specular)" />

            <!-- 展開先を示す点（青・緑のパルス） -->
            <g>
              <circle cx="332" cy="392" r="3.5" class="dot-blue" />
              <circle cx="332" cy="392" r="3.5" class="halo halo-blue">
                <animate attributeName="r" values="3.5;16" dur="3s" begin="0.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.5;0" dur="3s" begin="0.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
              </circle>
              <circle cx="196" cy="186" r="3.5" class="dot-green" />
              <circle cx="196" cy="186" r="3.5" class="halo halo-green">
                <animate attributeName="r" values="3.5;16" dur="3s" begin="1.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.5;0" dur="3s" begin="1.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
              </circle>
              <circle cx="168" cy="328" r="3" class="dot-blue" />
              <circle cx="168" cy="328" r="3" class="halo halo-blue">
                <animate attributeName="r" values="3;13" dur="3s" begin="2.4s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.45;0" dur="3s" begin="2.4s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
              </circle>
            </g>

            <!-- 導線 -->
            <path id="route" class="route-base"
              d="M 132 452 C 196 418, 214 372, 250 316 S 326 196, 384 142" />
            <use href="#route" class="route-flow" />
            <circle class="traveler" r="4">
              <animateMotion dur="6s" repeatCount="indefinite" rotate="0">
                <mpath href="#route" />
              </animateMotion>
            </circle>

            <!-- Spadyロゴ：導線の先でふわふわ漂い、点が届くとピカッと光る -->
            <g class="spady-sat">
              <circle cx="384" cy="142" r="56" fill="url(#flash)">
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0;0;0;1;0" keyTimes="0;0.88;0.93;0.96;1" dur="6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                <animate attributeName="r" values="34;34;34;62;70" keyTimes="0;0.88;0.93;0.96;1" dur="6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
              </circle>
              <circle cx="384" cy="142" r="33" class="sat-halo">
                <animate attributeName="r" values="33;48" dur="2.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0.5;0" dur="2.6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
              </circle>
              <circle cx="384" cy="142" r="33" class="sat-ring" />
              <image href="/logo.png?v=20260707-1519" x="352" y="110" width="64" height="64" clip-path="url(#satClip)" />
            </g>

            <!-- 地球を周回する人工衛星（金・青の2機） -->
            <g class="orbit-sat os-gold">
              <g>
                <rect x="-4.5" y="-3.5" width="9" height="7" rx="1.2" class="sat-body" />
                <rect x="-14" y="-2.5" width="8" height="5" rx="0.8" class="sat-panel" />
                <rect x="6" y="-2.5" width="8" height="5" rx="0.8" class="sat-panel" />
                <line x1="0" y1="-3.5" x2="0" y2="-8" class="sat-ant" />
                <circle cx="0" cy="-8.5" r="1.2" class="sat-ant-tip" />
              </g>
              <animateMotion dur="17s" repeatCount="indefinite" rotate="auto">
                <mpath href="#orbitPath" />
              </animateMotion>
            </g>
            <g class="orbit-sat os-blue">
              <g transform="scale(0.85)">
                <rect x="-4.5" y="-3.5" width="9" height="7" rx="1.2" class="sat-body" />
                <rect x="-14" y="-2.5" width="8" height="5" rx="0.8" class="sat-panel" />
                <rect x="6" y="-2.5" width="8" height="5" rx="0.8" class="sat-panel" />
                <line x1="0" y1="-3.5" x2="0" y2="-8" class="sat-ant" />
                <circle cx="0" cy="-8.5" r="1.2" class="sat-ant-tip" />
              </g>
              <animateMotion dur="17s" begin="-8.5s" repeatCount="indefinite" rotate="auto">
                <mpath href="#orbitPath" />
              </animateMotion>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Scroll cue -->
      <a class="scroll-cue rise d5" href="#problem" aria-label="Scroll down">
        <span class="sc-text">SCROLL</span>
        <span class="sc-circle">
          <svg class="sc-chev" viewBox="0 0 12 7" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 1l5 5 5-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" /></svg>
        </span>
      </a>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. 悩み -->
  <div class="band dark alt">
    <section class="lp-sec" id="problem">
      <div class="wrap narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow fade"><span class="e-dot"></span>PROBLEM</p>
        <h2 class="fade">Stuck in any of<br class="sp" /> these situations?</h2>
        <ul class="x-list">
          <li class="fade">You run ads, but they <b>never turn into inquiries, visits or sign-ups</b></li>
          <li class="fade">LINE friends keep growing, yet <b>all you send is mass broadcasts</b></li>
          <li class="fade">Ads, social and LINE are scattered and <b>nobody knows which one works</b></li>
          <li class="fade">You want to try Meta ads but <b>have no idea where to start</b></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="bridge fade">
          <p class="bridge-lead">Most of these problems aren't about talent or effort — they're about the <em>funnel</em>.</p>
          <p class="bridge-body">
            Daily walk-in business or long-consideration services — it makes no difference. Unless the entry points (ads, social) are connected to the receiving end (LINE, inquiries), results leak away mid-journey. Put the other way around: simply fixing the funnel changes a great deal.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. 強み -->
  <div class="band dark">
    <section class="lp-sec">
      <div class="wrap narrow">
        <p class="eyebrow fade"><span class="e-dot e-blue"></span>REASON</p>
        <h2 class="fade">If there's a reason<br class="sp" /> to talk to me</h2>
        <div class="reason fade">
          <span class="num">01</span>
          <div>
            <h3>I know ad platforms from the <em>inside</em></h3>
            <p>As a Marketing Pro at Meta (formerly Facebook), I supported ad operations for 80+ agencies in Japan. I design lean, waste-free campaigns from the platform's point of view.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reason fade">
          <span class="num">02</span>
          <div>
            <h3><em>100+ funnels</em> built in the field</h3>
            <p>From local shops to e-commerce, I have built 100+ LINE official accounts. For QQEnglish, one of Cebu's largest language schools, the study-abroad build was followed by its online English service. Every industry has its own distance to sign-up — I design for it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reason fade">
          <span class="num">03</span>
          <div>
            <h3>Ads, LINE and social — <em>designed as one</em></h3>
            <p>Hire a different vendor for each channel and the funnel breaks. I design the whole journey — from first touch to inquiry, consultation and sign-up.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. サービス -->
  <div class="band dark alt">
    <section class="lp-sec" id="lp-services">
      <!-- 浮遊する宇宙飛行士 -->
      <div class="astro-float" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 80 104">
          <rect x="22" y="34" width="36" height="34" rx="10" class="as-pack" />
          <rect x="26" y="30" width="28" height="42" rx="12" class="as-body" />
          <circle cx="40" cy="20" r="15" class="as-helmet" />
          <ellipse cx="40" cy="21" rx="10" ry="8.5" class="as-visor" />
          <ellipse cx="36" cy="18" rx="3" ry="2" class="as-glint" />
          <path d="M27 40 C16 44 12 52 14 60" class="as-limb" />
          <path d="M53 40 C64 42 70 38 72 30" class="as-limb" />
          <path d="M32 71 C30 80 26 88 22 92" class="as-limb" />
          <path d="M48 71 C52 80 56 86 62 88" class="as-limb" />
          <circle cx="40" cy="46" r="4" class="as-badge" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow fade"><span class="e-dot e-green"></span>SERVICE</p>
        <h2 class="fade">What I can help with</h2>
        <div class="grid2">
          <div class="card c-blue fade">
            <h3>Meta Ads Management</h3>
            <p>Strategy and hands-on management of Instagram & Facebook ads. Small test budgets welcome.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card c-blue fade">
            <h3>Meta Ads In-housing</h3>
            <p>Not outsourcing — coaching your team until you can run ads yourselves.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card c-green fade">
            <h3>LINE Official Account & L Message Build</h3>
            <p>Designed beyond the follow button: what to deliver, when, to whom. From JPY 300,000 (excl. tax).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card c-red fade">
            <h3>Social Media Support (Instagram / Threads)</h3>
            <p>A posting system your team can actually sustain, tailored to your business.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="industries fade">
          <span>Retail & F&amp;B</span><span>Beauty & Salons</span><span>Fitness</span><span>E-commerce</span><span>Education</span><span>Study-abroad</span><span>Global business</span><span>B2B</span>
        </div>
        <p class="note fade" style="margin-top: 20px;">Any industry is welcome.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. 実績（ロゴ入り） -->
  <div class="band dark">
    <section class="lp-sec" id="lp-works">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow fade"><span class="e-dot e-blue"></span>WORKS</p>
        <h2 class="fade">Selected work</h2>
        <div class="grid2">
          <div class="card work-card fade">
            <div class="logo-slot"><img src="/logo-qqenglish.png?v=20260707-1519" alt="QQEnglish" loading="lazy" /></div>
            <h3>QQEnglish (Cebu, Philippines)</h3>
            <p class="metric-lp">Study-abroad first — then online English, too</p>
            <p>Built the LINE accounts for one of Cebu's largest language schools. Two business lines, back to back.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card work-card fade">
            <div class="logo-slot"><img src="/logo-telenet.png?v=20260707-1519" alt="tele-net International" loading="lazy" /></div>
            <h3>tele-net International</h3>
            <p class="metric-lp">LINE build for a Japanese BPO serving global markets</p>
            <p>Built a business-card-style LINE official account, with in-LINE inquiry forms automatically linked to user profiles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mid-cta fade">
          <a class="btn primary btn-big" href="#contact">Book a Free Consultation</a>
          <p class="note" style="margin-top: 12px;">I'll review your current funnel and tell you exactly where to start.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- 6. 地域事業者の支援（第2の柱） -->
  <div class="band dark alt">
    <section class="lp-sec" id="local">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow fade"><span class="e-dot e-green"></span>LOCAL</p>
        <h2 class="fade">Local business support<span class="h2-sub">Hokkaido · Otaru/Zenibako</span></h2>
        <div class="seminar-grid">
          <div class="fade">
            <p class="lead">
              From my home base around Otaru, Zenibako and Sapporo, I help local shops and SMEs with Meta ads, LINE and social. Local or global, the job is the same: turning scattered tactics into one funnel.
            </p>
            <p class="note" style="margin-bottom: 4px;">
              I also host casual marketing and social media study sessions around Otaru — announced on Threads.
            </p>
          </div>
          <figure class="seminar-fig fade">
            <img src="/seminar.jpg?v=20260707-1519" alt="A study session in Otaru" loading="lazy" width="1080" height="1080" />
            <figcaption>A study session in Otaru</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- 8. プロフィール -->
  <div class="band dark alt">
    <section class="lp-sec" id="profile">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow fade"><span class="e-dot"></span>PROFILE</p>
        <div class="lp-profile fade">
          <div class="lp-profile-mark"><img src="/profile.jpg?v=20260707-1519" alt="Hiroshi Inoue" width="320" height="320" /></div>
          <div>
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 6px;">Hiroshi Inoue</h2>
            <p class="note" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Founder, Spady｜Otaru, Hokkaido, Japan</p>
            <p>
              As a Marketing Pro at Meta (formerly Facebook), I supported ad operations for 80+ agencies in Japan. Since going independent, I have built 100+ LINE official accounts — from local shops to global businesses, including QQEnglish, one of Cebu's largest language schools. Around my home base in Otaru, I also support local businesses and host study sessions.
            </p>
            <div class="profile-links">
            <a class="threads-chip" href="https://www.threads.com/hiroshiinoue.spady" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Follow Hiroshi Inoue on Threads">
